org.cloudgraph.store.key

Interface MetaKey

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EdgeMetaKey, EntityMetaKey, GraphMetaKey

    public interface MetaKey
    Qualifier or code-set used to describe a graph/row.

    The name is referenced directly in source code, and the underlying code is used as the actual physical column qualifier. The allows the source to remain more readable while allowing more terse physical qualifiers or column keys.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
